## 📢 Results & Insights  
🔹 Senior male citizens using **electronic check payments** have a higher churn rate.  
🔹 Customers with **tenure > 70 months** or **monthly charges > $100** are more likely to churn.  
🔹 Customers with **two-year contracts** and **mailed check payments** churn less frequently.  
🔹 **Random Forest** achieved the highest accuracy in churn prediction.  

---

